Package municipalities

Class Summary
MunicipalitiesRecord MunicipalitiesRecord contains a set of Municipality and is used to manage, access and search them.
Municipality Municipality is used to store informations regarding a Town's Municipality.
TestMunicipalities TestMunicipalities is used to test in console mode the behavior of the MunicipalitiesRecord.
 

Exception Summary
MunicipalityAlreadyExistsException An MunicipalityAlreadyExistsException is an exception indicating that an operation failed because a MunicipalitiesRecord already contained an identical Municipality.
NoSuchDirectoryException An NoSuchDirectoryException is an exception indicating that an operation failed because the path given was not valid, or the directory did not exist.
NoSuchMunicipalityException An NoSuchMunicipalityException is an exception indicating that an operation failed because a MunicipalitiesRecord did not contained an Municipality by the name specified.
